    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raybounder</strong> is a top-down puzzle shooter where you are armed with a unique laser gun that is both a tool for navigation and device for destruction. Master the gun's movement and ricocheting lasers to navigate increasingly complex and challenging environments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ricochet Lasers</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically position your gun and unleash beams that bounce off walls, hit targets and destroy enemies, clearing a path to the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/b0a126a3cd42f543ccf1241f31fba584.avif?t=1766035872\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Unique, Versatile Weapon</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw your laser gun across gaps, locomote using recoil, dispatch enemies and activate distant switches to unlock new areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/c1515d9bb4f953c58c1537bf7a654b28.poster.avif?t=1766035872\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/c1515d9bb4f953c58c1537bf7a654b28.webm?t=1766035872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/c1515d9bb4f953c58c1537bf7a654b28.mp4?t=1766035872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging and Varied Environments</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect gears, unlock cosmetics, and earn achievements across 12+ biomes and 60+ levels.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/7154c76e5c4b311a41171c9b451d1b06.apng?t=1766035872\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326580/extras/7154c76e5c4b311a41171c9b451d1b06.poster.avif?t=1766035872\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=192 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect your aim, master your throws, and prove your mettle in <strong>Raybounder!</strong></p>",
